&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot;&gt;Shape the creative vision for large-scale, long-term solutions, from immersive campaign sites to brand platforms, content ecosystems, products, and tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot;&gt;Design at the highest level by staying hands-on in Figma to shape screens, components, and systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot;&gt;Translate brand strategy and business objectives into functional user journeys, flows, states, and motion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,0&quot;&gt;Use AI fluently across the creative process for ideation, image creation, motion, voice, code, and prototyping.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0&quot;&gt;Move from sketches to working prototypes quickly using Figma, code, AI tools, and rapid-build environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,5,0&quot;&gt;Look beyond the core product to fuse the full ecosystem of content, campaigns, and related technologies into a seamless brand experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,6,0&quot;&gt;Direct multidisciplinary teams across art direction, copy, and design while protecting the central idea from kickoff to launch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,7,0&quot;&gt;Mentor designers and creatives by providing the direction, feedback, and room they need to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
