&lt;li&gt;Full professional fluency in both English and Mandarin Chinese is mandatory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a proven ability to manage, inspire, and grow diverse teams of creatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re a genuine sports fan who is as skilled at elevated product storytelling as you are at driving social and community engagement around athletes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A body of work that demonstrates mastery across everything from high-end TVC and KV production to innovative social-first campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional presentation skills with a track record of winning pitches and building strong client relationships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
